⚠️ TeamFight Tactics content and materials are trademarks and copyrights of Riot and its licensors. All rights reserved. This application is not affiliated with Riot. ⚠️

Upgrade your skill to TFT, the Riot autochess in the League of Legends universe.

💥 Craft best objects with the basic items you own.

💥 Display details of objects if you have doubts about their capacity.

💥 Display help with choice of item on the carousel to obtain top-tiers items.

💥 Anticipate your team composition with the table of champions grouped by origins and classes.

💥 Equip your highest-level champion in the most optimal way to turn him into a monster with the recommended items for each character.

💥 Access all the best team compositions and optimal placements of your champions
